caption.title: Viruses isolated from severe/fatal outcome influenza-infected patients have low DVGs numbers.
caption.p: DVGs proportions, calculated as jumping reads per million (RPM) that align the viral genome, found in virions isolated from influenza A virus infected patients. Severe/fatal-case viruses, SF1-SF6; Mild-case viruses, M1-M6.
